  "story": {
    "title": "The Calm Village Lesson",
    "body": "In a small village, people lived a calm and peaceful life. Rafi was a friendly boy who frequently walked around the village and greeted everyone. One day, the teacher gave a school project. The students had to describe their village and write a report. Rafi tried to behave in an appropriate way and followed every instruction carefully. At first, he was nervous and expected he might fail. But he stayed calm and worked with positive thinking. He often visited the library to solve problems and understand topics better. His teacher did not punish anyone but helped them improve. During the project, Rafi learned that patience and good habits are very important. He represented his village in the school presentation. Everyone was surprised by his confidence. In the end, he got a good grade and felt content. It was a simple village life story, but it taught a big lesson.",
    "comprehension": [
      {
        "q": "Where did Rafi live?",
        "opts": ["city", "village", "forest", "school"],
        "ans": 1
      },
